    "content": "<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 12pt; line-height: 19.5pt; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white; font-weight: normal;\">尊敬的商家朋友</span>：</strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; line-height: inherit; margin: inherit; padding: inherit; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: inherit; padding: inherit; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: inherit; padding: inherit; max-width: 100%;\">您好，为适应业务发展需求，将修订《<a style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: inherit; padding: inherit; color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1211622812805107712\">京东开放平台个人/个体经营类目商品阈值明细表</a>》，现进行规则修订公示，公示期：2026年5月13日- 2026年5月19日，规则预计于 2026年5月20日生效，公示期满平台将另行发布正式生效规则。</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: inherit !important; padding: inherit !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">核心调整点：部分二级类目的商品阈值数量调整</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: inherit !important; padding: inherit !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">具体修订内容如下：</span></span></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"width: 276.0pt; border-collapse: collapse;\" border=\"0\" width=\"368\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 14pt; background-color: #ced4d9;\">\n<td style=\"width: 52.0pt; border: solid black 1.0pt; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.0pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"69\">&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 52.0pt; border: solid black 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.0pt;\" width=\"69\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 8.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">一级类目</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 120.0pt; border: solid black 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.0pt;\" width=\"160\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 8.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">二级类目</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 52.0pt; border: solid black 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.0pt;\" width=\"69\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 8.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">类目阈值</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 52.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.0pt;\" width=\"69\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">调整前</span></p>\n</td>\n<td